WEBVTT

00:01.046 --> 00:03.086
<i>Previously on</i>
Falling Skies...

00:03.111 --> 00:05.407
I was in school
when the ships came.

00:06.721 --> 00:08.274
All electronics stop working.

00:08.299 --> 00:11.521
They killed grown-ups,
and they catch kids.

00:12.845 --> 00:13.657
Get off.

00:13.682 --> 00:16.820
We cannot fight these things
unless we know how.

00:18.054 --> 00:19.158
Ben.

00:19.183 --> 00:20.774
He's alive.
We got to go get him.

00:20.799 --> 00:22.093
They die, just like us.

00:22.702 --> 00:24.333
Just got to get close.

00:25.655 --> 00:28.173
I thought you were all
just a bunch of strangers

00:28.198 --> 00:29.701
thrown together by fate.

00:31.305 --> 00:33.081
Ships are gonna target
the flares.

00:34.415 --> 00:36.119
Well, I guess you got me
after all.

00:36.144 --> 00:37.649
I said you could go look
for your son.

00:37.674 --> 00:39.038
Do you have any idea
where he is?

00:39.063 --> 00:41.622
Margaret -- she saw some
harnessed kids out by a hospital.

00:41.647 --> 00:42.547
What if it's a trap?

00:42.560 --> 00:44.859
Go to the van. Don't wait for us.
You go, and you go fast.

